text: Élie Bourgois (5 January 1881 - 2 June 1946) was a French gymnast. He competed in the men's individual all-around event at the 1900 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1881 births Category:1946 deaths Category:French male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of France Category:Gymnasts at the 1900 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Roubaix
